                        <interp inst="t18341205-name-442" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN NICHOLSON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 18.) I was called—I saw the prisoner coming out of the shop—I took him, and he dropped this bacon.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I did not take it—I had some tea and sugar in my apron. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> He had two small parcels beside the bacon.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had been at work all day for my father, and he sent me for tea-and sugar, and other things—I went into this man's shop for some butter—I touched this bacon, and it fell down.</p>
